Actress-turned-politician, Tonto Dikeh has lamented losing over 800 of her poultry chicks to flood. The running mate for Tonye Ibraye, African Democratic Congress (ADC) via an Instagram post, said she only just came to the realisation of the huge loss that had befallen her poultry on Friday morning as a result of the flooding.   I don’t mind staying single for life – Beauty     I’ve an albino twin brother – Daniella     Drag anyone on Apostle Suleiman’s alleged s3x list – Yul…   Lamenting her loss, Tontolet declared her identity as a “chosen” but wondered what the flood’s was. She wrote: “Woke up to the sad reality of this raining season #Flood. Lost over 800 of my #Poultry babies..All I can say is I AM A CHOSEN. I AM A CHOSEN. FLOOD WHO ARE YOU?”